I learned yesterday , after inquiries in Fairport , that you were the owner of this vessel . 
The real estate person from whom you purchased it assured me that you were financially responsible . 
I came to expose this imposter and to recover my box . 
On my way hither I was caught in the storm . 
The runaway occurred , and you know the rest . 
Miss Pringle , during this recital , had not deigned to favor Lady Agatha with a look . 
Lady Agatha , on her part , after the rebuff which she had received , had sat in smiling silence . 
